	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Those are gerbers. Exports. You want whatever project file generated them. Those are meant to be sent to a PCB manufacturer. GerbView will let you take a look at them. I've never heard of GC-Prevue, but from the name, it looks like it's for previewing gerbers. Maybe some wonderful software exists to facilitate the editing of gerbers, but they aren't mean to be worked on.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


