		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know Gerber files have <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Turner_Cook" class="postlink">nothing</a> to do with Brandy O'Bannon mystery novels. But in this analogy, would a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gerber_format" class="postlink">Gerber file</a> be analogous to a PDF?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
